{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/front-end-development-libraries/bootstrap/ditch-custom-css-for-bootstrap","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"bootstrap","demoType":null,"title":"Uklonite prilagođeni CSS za Bootstrap","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Možemo čistiti naš kod i učiniti da naša Aplikacija za slike mačaka izgleda više kao ugovor koristeći Bootstrap stilove umesto prilagođenih stilova koje smo prvobitno kreirali.</p>\n<p>Nemojte brinjati - biće mnogo vremena za prilagođavanje našeg CSS-a kasnije.</p>\n<p>Uklonite deklaracije <code>.red-text</code>, <code>p</code> i <code>.smaller-image</code> iz vašeg <code>style</code> elementa tako da jedine deklaracije koje ostanu u vašem <code>style</code> elementu budu <code>h2</code> i <code>thick-green-border</code>.</p>\n<p>Zatim uklonite <code>p</code> element sa mrtvim linkom. Zatim uklonite klasu <code>red-text</code> iz vašeg <code>h2</code> elementa i zamenite je Bootstrap klasom <code>text-primary</code>.</p>\n<p>Na kraju, uklonite klasu <code>smaller-image</code> sa vašeg prvog <code>img</code> elementa i zamenite je klasom <code>img-responsive</code>.</p>\n</section>","id":"bad87fee1347bd9aedf08845","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":0,"helpCategory":"HTML-CSS","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"front-end-development-libraries","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":17565,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/front-end-development-libraries/bootstrap/ditch-custom-css-for-bootstrap"},"required":[{"link":"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/twitter-bootstrap/3.3.7/css/bootstrap.css","src":null}],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"indexhtml","ext":"html","name":"index","contents":"<link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Lobster\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\">\r\n<style>\r\n  .red-text {\r\n    color: red;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  h2 {\r\n    font-family: Lobster, Monospace;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  p {\r\n    font-size: 16px;\r\n    font-family: Monospace;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  .thick-green-border {\r\n    border-color: green;\r\n    border-width: 10px;\r\n    border-style: solid;\r\n    border-radius: 50%;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  .smaller-image {\r\n    width: 100px;\r\n  }\r\n</style>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"container-fluid\">\r\n  <h2 class=\"red-text text-center\">CatPhotoApp</h2>\r\n\r\n  <p>Click here for <a href=\"#\">cat photos</a>.</p>\r\n\r\n  <a href=\"#\"><img class=\"smaller-image thick-green-border\" src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/relaxing-cat.jpg\" alt=\"A cute orange cat lying on its back.\"></a>\r\n\r\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/running-cats.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive\" alt=\"Tuxedo cats running on dirt ground.\">\r\n  <div class=\"row\">\r\n    <div class=\"col-xs-4\">\r\n      <button class=\"btn btn-block btn-primary\">Like</button>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"col-xs-4\">\r\n      <button class=\"btn btn-block btn-info\">Info</button>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"col-xs-4\">\r\n      <button class=\"btn btn-block btn-danger\">Delete</button>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n  <p>Things cats love:</p>\r\n  <ul>\r\n    <li>catnip</li>\r\n    <li>laser pointers</li>\r\n    <li>lasagna</li>\r\n  </ul>\r\n  <p>Top 3 things cats hate:</p>\r\n  <ol>\r\n    <li>flea treatment</li>\r\n    <li>thunder</li>\r\n    <li>other cats</li>\r\n  </ol>\r\n  <form action=\"https://freecatphotoapp.com/submit-cat-photo\">\r\n    <label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"indoor-outdoor\"> Indoor</label>\r\n    <label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"indoor-outdoor\"> Outdoor</label>\r\n    <label><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"personality\"> Loving</label>\r\n    <label><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"personality\"> Lazy</label>\r\n    <label><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"personality\"> Crazy</label>\r\n    <input type=\"text\" placeholder=\"cat photo URL\" required>\r\n    <button type=\"submit\">Submit</button>\r\n  </form>\r\n</div>","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["index.html"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Vaš <code>h2</code> element više ne bi trebalo da ima klasu <code>red-text</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.isFalse(document.querySelector('h2')?.classList?.contains('red-text'));"},{"text":"<p>Vaš <code>h2</code> element sada bi trebalo da ima klasu <code>text-primary</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.isTrue(document.querySelector('h2')?.classList?.contains('text-primary'));"},{"text":"<p>Vaši paragrafi više ne bi trebalo da koriste font <code>Monospace</code>.</p>","testString":"const paragraphElement = document.querySelector('p');\r\nconst paragraphFontFamily = window.getComputedStyle(paragraphElement)[\"font-family\"]; \r\nassert.notMatch(paragraphFontFamily,/monospace/i);"},{"text":"<p>Klasa <code>smaller-image</code> bi trebalo da bude uklonjena sa vaše gornje slike.</p>","testString":"assert.isFalse(document.querySelector('img')?.classList?.contains('smaller-image'));"},{"text":"<p>Trebalo bi da dodate klasu <code>img-responsive</code> na vašu gornju sliku.</p>","testString":"assert.lengthOf(document.querySelectorAll('.img-responsive'),2);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/front-end-development-libraries/#bootstrap","dashedName":"ditch-custom-css-for-bootstrap","certification":"front-end-development-libraries","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"front-end-development-libraries","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"bootstrap","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[{"link":"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/twitter-bootstrap/3.3.7/css/bootstrap.css","src":null}],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/front-end-development-libraries/bootstrap/use-a-span-to-target-inline-elements","prevChallengePath":"/learn/front-end-development-libraries/bootstrap/use